      "date": "2011-10-30 01:11:39.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on rhel/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/b8133c9e-0292-11e1-88e4-52540025f9af).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
